    "date": "2023-06-20T17:40:07Z",
    "text": "Secure America's Financial Exchanges Act or the SAFE Act \n\nThis bill requires an issuer of securities, as a condition of listing its securities on a national exchange, to disclose (1) any financial support from China and the terms of any such support, and (2) whether any officer or director holds or previously held a position with the Chinese government or with the Chinese Communist Party."
